Which were the 10 most observed species?

The 10 most commonly observed species of bird by the Feeder Watch community over winter 2020/21

Species Name Number of Observations
Spinus pinus 1125
Acanthis flammea 705
Zenaida macroura 394
Cyanocitta cristata 327
Cardinalis cardinalis 263
Branta canadensis 223
Haemorhous purpureus 214
Spinus tristis 179
Haemorhous mexicanus 176
Anas platyrhynchos 171
